)\">Alma 10:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106724\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106724)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106724)\">Ps. 49:2<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114100\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114100)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114100)\">D&amp;C 58:47<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111264\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111264)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111264)\">2 Ne. 26:33<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"117112\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 117112)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(117112)\">JS&mdash;H 1:22,75<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109240\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109240)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109240)\">Rom. 2:3<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108945\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108945)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108945)\">Acts 2:38<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112599\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112599)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112599)\">3 Ne. 11:25<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113371\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113371)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113371)\">D&amp;C 20:41<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113582\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113582)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113582)\">D&amp;C 33:15<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114440\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114440)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114440)\">D&amp;C 76:52<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114023\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114023)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114023)\">D&amp;C 53:3<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114028\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114028)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114028)\">D&amp;C 55:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114441\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114441)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114441)\">D&amp;C 76:52<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">18. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109220\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109220)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109220)\">Rom. 1:2<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111960\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111960)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111960)\">Alma 14:8<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113340\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113340)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113340)\">D&amp;C 20:11,35,69<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113589\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113589)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113589)\">D&amp;C 33:16<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">19. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112704\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112704)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112704)\">3 Ne. 27:20<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">20. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114554\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114554)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114554)\">D&amp;C 78:7<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114820\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114820)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114820)\">D&amp;C 88:22<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">21. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107387\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107387)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107387)\">Jer. 31:31<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110231\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110231)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110231)\">Heb. 8:8,13<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113412\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113412)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113412)\">D&amp;C 22:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114709\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114709)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114709)\">D&amp;C 84:57<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">22. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"117186\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 117186)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(117186)\">A of F 1:4<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">23. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110503\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110503)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110503)\">2 Pet. 1:5-8<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}